dct_title_s: The world, physical / produced by the Cartographic Division, National Geographic Society ; John F. Shupe, chief cartographer.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, gradient tints, and spot heights. Depths shown by contours, shading, gradient tints, and soundings. Lists of: Earth's extremes and areas (in square miles). Includes 6 inset maps, abbreviations and statistical data. Ancillary maps: North polar region [physical] -- South polar region [physical] -- Vital statistics -- Earth's crust -- Currents -- Winds.
